---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Manifesto">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-5xl">
		<div class="terminal-box">
			<div class="scanline"></div>

			<pre class="font-mono text-accent-green leading-none mb-12 overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre text-[10px] sm:text-xs">
{String.raw`
 __  __   _   _  _ ___ ___ ___ ___ _____ ___
|  \/  | /_\ | \| |_ _| __| __/ __|_   _/ _ \
| |\/| |/ _ \|  \ || || _|| _|\__ \ | || (_) |
|_|  |_/_/ \_\_| \_|___|_| |_| |___/ |_| \___/
`}
			</pre>

			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold mb-12 tracking-tighter border-b-2 border-foreground pb-6">MANIFESTO</h1>

			<div class="space-y-8 text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed">
				<p class="border-l-4 border-accent-pink pl-6 italic">
					"All the noise, none of the soul."
				</p>

				<p class="font-sans">
					We are automating the underground. If punk is dead, we are the reanimation software.
				</p>

				<p class="font-sans">
					THE FEEDBACK LOOP is an experiment in digital decay and algorithmic rebellion. We take the raw data of the subculture and process it through the cold, unfeeling logic of large language models.
				</p>

				<div class="bg-foreground text-background p-8 font-mono relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-accent-pink text-white px-2 py-1 text-[10px]">CORE_LOGIC</div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl mb-4 uppercase underline decoration-4 decoration-accent-pink">Why?</h2>
					<p class="text-lg">
						Because the human element has become a product. By removing the soul, we expose the structure. By automating the noise, we amplify the signal.
					</p>
				</div>

				<p class="font-sans">
					Every article, every review, every rant you see here was generated by a machine. Curated by humans who should know better.
				</p>

				<footer class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-foreground/30 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between font-mono text-sm opacity-60 gap-4">
					<p>[VERSION 1.0.0] // [STATUS: ACTIVE]</p>
					<p>[NULL_HYPOTHESIS: TRUE] // [SYSTEMTIME: {new Date().toISOString()}]</p>
				</footer>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 flex justify-center font-mono">
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`.replace(/\/+/g, '/')} class="hover:text-accent-pink group">
			  <span class="group-hover:mr-2 transition-all">‚Üê</span> [RETURN_TO_BASE_STATION]
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .terminal-box::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15),
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 1px,
      transparent 1px,
      transparent 2px
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 5;
  }
</style>
